    "date": "2024-01-11T13:51:49Z",
    "text": "Ending Forced Arbitration of Race Discrimination Act of 2023 \n\nThis bill prohibits a predispute arbitration agreement from being valid or enforceable with respect to a case relating to a race discrimination dispute at the election of the person alleging the discrimination."
